name: contending hegemonies
description:
november 10th 2021

armada of condensed ceramic
nanometals, self repairing hulls.
ion backthrusters, leisure speed…
blue laser turrets all turn
in same direction 
and fire!
what a light show
for the green-skinned envoy
from Averia Commandant,
that star empire light years away.

---
